column2: Too many men, both famous and not, have had their lives, reputations and careers damaged or destroyed due to accusations (most without any proof) made by women. How is a man or woman convicted for rape, verbal or physical assault - 1. Before a civil or criminal case has even started  2. With absolutely no evidence, no witnesses or anything. I am a domestic abuse survivor (not physical, but mental abuse). Women who claim domestic abuse for personal, financial, or retaliatory gain make me furious, they're going to make it that much more difficult in the long run for actual victims to be believed

column34: As a nation we must do better and support ALL domestic violence victims . Johnny Depp is a man of good moral character and his on screen presence needs no introduction . We must stop believing only women can be victims . Mr. Depp and his legal team have proven that Amber heard has told many false truths regarding his alleged physical abuse of her . Hollywood and it’s presence has effectively forgotten to support this man . It’s a complete outrage. Please help In restoring the belief in his career and Character as a man beloved by ALL.
